  "text": "This general method follows on from the Shadowboard Methodology by Goschnick and Graham [CITATION_1] . It was not a generic AO methodology, but was specifically aimed at gathering and tailoring the AO requirements for a multi-agent Personal Assistant Agent (PAA) system, for an individual user. The authors made the point with:",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "8982832"
